      "content": "everything just feels so heavy lately. like my soul is too big for this body or something. i lost my sister last month and now nothing feels real. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but i don't know what. is this just how life is supposed to be? is this pain actually supposed to be part of some bigger plan?",
